  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether a rehabilitation program following lumbar
      microdiscectomy influences short-term (4 months) and long-term (up to 5 years)outcomes in
      quality of life, activity and endurance.
    </textblock>
